{
  "title": "ISic003174. I.Sicily inscription 003174",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[ἐπὶ γυμνασ]ι̣άρχων <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> τοῦ] <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τιμαίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τιμαίου\">Τιμαίου</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] τοῦ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τίμωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τίμωνος\">Τίμωνος</span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[οἱ ἀλειφόμε]νο[ι] <br id=\"al4a-interpretive\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[.........].ΑΡΧΩΝ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>...]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τιμαίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τιμαίου\">ΤΙΜΑΙΟΥ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΤΟΥ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τίμωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τίμωνος\">ΤΙΜΩΝΟΣ</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[..........]ΝΟ[.]<br id=\"al4a-diplomatic\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Manganaro 1999</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Cultrera: [--- φυ]λάρχων</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Manganaro's restoration is necessarily speculative, but the overall construction, magistracy and names, seems reasonably certain. Cultrera's proposal was more arbitrary and does not reflect the traces on the stone in line 1.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 49.1331.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 14.0580 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 1953.0281 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> Cultrera 1951 809 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002062\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002062</a></li><li> Manganaro 1999 67 no.58 fig.140 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813</a></li><li> Dimartino 2009 211 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002021\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002021</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
